##### Authentication
### Login
POST {{URL}}/authentication/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

### Logout
POST {{URL}}/authentication/logout

### Get user information
GET {{URL}}/authentication

### Sign up
PUT {{URL}}/authentication
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "test",
  "username": "test",
  "password": "test",
  "affiliation": "test",
  "email": "test",
  "webPage": "test"
}


