##### User management
### List users
GET {{URL}}/users

### Update type and validation
PUT {{URL}}/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": 1,
  "validated": true
}

##### Paper submissioon
### Get paper
GET {{URL}}/paper

### Submit proposal
POST {{URL}}/paper
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "text",
  "field": "text",
  "keywords": "text",
  "topics": "text",
  "abstract": "text",
  "authors": [
    {
      "name": "author1",
      "email": "author1Email"
    },
    {
      "name": "author2",
      "email": "author2Email"
    }
  ]
}

### Upload abstract for paper with id 1
PUT {{URL}}/paper
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paperId": 1,
  "abstract": "text"
}

### Upload full paper for id 1
PUT {{URL}}/paper/full/1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data